3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或30萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e5%af%a9%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c89%2c20220401%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,審交簡,89,20220401,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"審交簡","JNO":"89","JDATE":"20220401","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}